ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectOrder No. 163 - (Alberta) Provincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 163 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the federal government to provide financial assistance to the province of ALBERTA with respect to the FLOODING causing damage to private property and provincial and municipal infrastructure in the City of Calgary from June 5 to 6, 2012.
